            "title": "盤中速報 - 擎亞(8096)股價拉至漲停，漲停價64.2元，成交44,860張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>擎亞(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8096:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8096\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8096-TW</a>)28日11:18上漲5.8元，股價漲停報64.2元，委買33,000張、委賣2,246,000張，成交44,860張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為國際貿易業。電子材料批發業。智慧財產權業。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>擎亞(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8096:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8096\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8096-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲14.06%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲2.57%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+5,131 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+4,678 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+453 張</li> <li>融資增減：+1,226 張</li> <li>融券增減：+236 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
