 rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8358-TW</a>)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>CPO：環宇 - KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4991:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4991\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4991-TW</a>)、IET-KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4971:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4971\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4971-TW</a>)、聯亞 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3081:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3081\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3081-TW</a>)、上詮 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3363:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3363\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3363-TW</a>)、波若威 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3163:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3163\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3163-TW</a>)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>個股詳細解析：</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>漢磊 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3707:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3707\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3707-TW</a>)：SiC、GaN 的磊晶與晶圓代工服務。應用於 AI、電動車、綠能高壓元件的代工服務。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"m